strings.Value: "Hey, I'm outta rations! I got to hit the sack hungry tonight, or what?!"
"Hey, I got no more chow! Anyone has an extra ration? Want to share?"
"Take mine. I don't feel hungry today."
"I'll gladly share my rations with you, Amiri. After all, I'm trying to watch my figure!"
"I'm feeling generous tonight. You can take my ration. Don't forget to say thank you â€” and don't try to eat my stationery."
"Nothing improves one's appetite more than the envious looks of the starving."
